\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 The other notes, shown greyed-out, may stay in the default voice 0 for that staff.  Notice there are no voice 0 notes in the top staff in the bar.  The highlighted notes cannot be assigned to voice 0 because the last four eighth-notes are actually attached to the lower staff, which already has a voice 0 in motion.  This is not the only way to notate this example, as we shall see in a moment.\par
